Mini Project Overview

Youâ€™ll build a Python Flask web app that connects to a MySQL database, and it will be served through Nginx, all orchestrated via Docker Compose.
Finally, youâ€™ll push the Flask app image to Docker Hub.

âš™ï¸ Step 1: Project Structure

Create a folder:
