Inside it, create this structure:

docker-mini-project/
â”œâ”€â”€ app/
â”‚   â”œâ”€â”€ app.py
â”‚   â”œâ”€â”€ requirements.txt
â”‚   â””â”€â”€ Dockerfile
â”œâ”€â”€ nginx/
