Now open:
ğŸ‘‰ http://localhost:8080

(or http://<your-public-IP>:8080 on EC2)

You should see:

â€œHello from Flask App running with Docker Compose!â€

â˜ï¸ Step 7: Push Flask Image to Docker Hub

